data.description: This 2 year old beautiful townhome is waiting on you to rent! This home offers a stunning first floor open floor plan. Enjoy preparing meals in this open kitchen overlooking your living/dining area . Second floor laundry room. One car garage. Prime Central Location just MINUTES to Numerous Shopping Destinations, Restaurants, Parks, Golf Courses- And SO Much More! Convenient Access to Major Traffic Arteries I-695, 95 & 83. 20 minutes to BWI Airport, 35 Minutes to Annapolis, & 50 minutes to Washington, D.C.
